item.title: US-19E North at US-321/TN-67 - Hampton
item.description: US-19E North at US-321/TN-67 in Hampton. Turn right for US-321 South/TN-67 East to Mountain City and Boone NC. Continue straight for US-19E/US-321 North/TN-67 West.

item.title: US-19E North at US-321 and TN-67
item.description: US-19E North at US-321 and TN-67 in Hampton. Turn right for US-321 South/TN-67 East. Continue straight for US-321 north. US-321 North joins US-19E northbound.

item.title: End TNS-173 East at US-19E
item.description: End TNS-173 East at US-19E in Carter County.

item.title: End TNS-173 North at US-19E
item.description: End TNS-173 North at US-19E. Use US-19E south for Roan Mountain; US-19E north for Elizabethton.
